modName: Daenerys Targaryen RaceMenu Preset- Game of Thrones -FIXED-
descriptionHtml:
Touched up the face, changed the hair, & most importantly fixed the issue of Daenerys's body just turning pure white or purple.

Check out Shorsey's original version here - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/69023/?

If you have any bugs, issues, suggestions, etc, let me know. I'm extremely new to modding, so any help would be awesome.
